from craige craig eid subject candlestick park experience long i be a giant season ticket holder for year and never really complain about the old ballyard place sure it be cold the food line be long and the hire hand be surly but thi wa all part of the giant mystique or so i think i go to tuesday game giant over the marlin and the wa a much different place nothing short of a dome will eliminate the wind but everything be a lot better the line be a lot shorter the bathroom be clean and have run water and the hire hand be very polite the new foghorn light up and blow after each homerun and the wooden fence be very nice a be the new bleacher the bleacher start right at the top of the fence and give a great view and they get beer stand at the bottome of the bleacher the only complaint be that the electronic old-fashioned scoreboard look electronic could be better these thing should have be do a long time ago but it take a real businessman ex safeway president peter magowan to figure it out just like he use to tell hi checker if the customer do come back i do need a many checker thi be a knock on bob lurie he wa a competent businessman but he do deal much with the general public i give an example of how the level of service ha change the onion dispenser jam a i wa use it an attendant come over apoligized for the problem and proceed to fix the machine after he wa do he clean the machine and say he wa glad to be able to help in the old day there wa no attendant and the folk at the concession stand would say go to the stand foot away they might be able to help all in all it wa a fun day craig eid e-mail addres craige 